#: ../../source/comparison.md:1
msgid "When to use IR-SIM"
msgstr "何时使用 IR-SIM"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:3
msgid ""
"IR-SIM occupies a specific niche: a **lightweight, pure-Python, YAML-driven "
"2D simulator** for navigation, control, and reinforcement learning. This "
"page explains where it shines and where another tool is the better choice, "
"so you can pick the right simulator for your problem."
msgstr ""
"IR-SIM 占据着一个特定的细分领域：一款**轻量、纯 Python、以 YAML 驱动的 2D "
"仿真器**，面向导航、控制与强化学习。本页说明它的优势所在，以及在什么情况下另一种工具更合适，帮助你为自己的问题选对仿真器。"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:5
msgid "A good fit when you want to"
msgstr "在以下情况它很合适"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:7
msgid ""
"**Prototype and benchmark** navigation, control, or RL algorithms in 2D, "
"quickly."
msgstr "**快速原型与基准测试** 2D 中的导航、控制或强化学习算法。"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:8
msgid ""
"**Describe scenes declaratively** in YAML — iterate fast, version-control "
"scenarios, and share them."
msgstr "**以声明式方式描述场景**（YAML）—— 快速迭代、对场景进行版本控制并分享。"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:9
msgid ""
"Run **multi-agent** experiments with built-in collision-avoidance behaviors "
"(RVO, ORCA, SFM)."
msgstr "运行**多智能体**实验，内置避碰行为（RVO、ORCA、SFM）。"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:10
msgid ""
"Stay **pure-Python and pip-installable**, with minimal dependencies and no "
"GPU."
msgstr "保持**纯 Python、可 pip 安装**，依赖极少且无需 GPU。"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:12
msgid "Reach for another tool when you need"
msgstr "在以下情况请选择其他工具"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:14
msgid ""
"**High-fidelity 3D physics**, contact dynamics, or manipulation → Gazebo, "
"MuJoCo, or NVIDIA Isaac Sim."
msgstr "**高保真 3D 物理**、接触动力学或机械臂操作 → Gazebo、MuJoCo 或 NVIDIA Isaac Sim。"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:15
msgid "**Photorealistic sensors** or autonomous-driving scenes → CARLA."
msgstr "**拟真传感器**或自动驾驶场景 → CARLA。"

#: ../../source/comparison.md:16
msgid ""
"A tightly **ROS-integrated** robot stack for sim-to-real → Gazebo with ROS."
msgstr "面向 sim-to-real 的紧密 **ROS 集成**机器人栈 → 搭配 ROS 的 Gazebo。"

